        "subject": "LU-3470 llog: fix return value of llog_alloc_handle",
        "message": "LU-3470 llog: fix return value of llog_alloc_handle\n\nllog_open() calls llog_alloc_handle() taking NULL as the error return\nvalue. But llog_alloc_handle() returns ERR_PTR(-ENOMEM) instead when\ntriggered.\n\nThis patch is ported from master based on patch 6644 by Li Xi.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobbie Lind <bobbie.j.lind@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1aa1c9d5011ec86a0d35b4e4a64ef73591c4ba34\n"
